headline: Teradyne (TER) Is Up 5.9% After UltraPHY 224G Launch—Has the Bull Case Changed?
summary: In September 2025, Teradyne announced the release of the UltraPHY 224G for UltraFLEXplus, setting a new standard in high-speed physical layer (PHY) performance testing for semiconductor manufacturing, data centers, and silicon photonics. This breakthrough expands Teradyne's testing solutions portfolio, allowing customers to address both current and emerging high-speed interface needs on a single, scalable platform. headline: Teradyne Unveils Titan HP
summary: NORTH READING, Mass., October 02, 2025--Teradyne announced the launch of its Titan HP system level test platform, designed specifically for AI and cloud infrastructure devices.
